1. Vi *izlazite* iz kuće uvek u isto vreme. (You *exit* the house at the same time every day.)
2. Izvinite, *izlazite* li vi iz ove prodavnice? (Excuse me, are you *leaving* this store?)
3. *Izlazite* iz automobila, molim vas. (Please *get out* of the car.)
4. Nemojte *izlaziti* vani bez kišobrana. (Don't *go out* without an umbrella.)
5. Oni ne *izlaze* često na večere. (They don't *go out* for dinner often.)
6. Da li *izlazite* u grad večeras? (Are you *going out* in the city tonight?)
7. Kada *izlaziš* iz bolnice? (When are you *being discharged* from the hospital?)
8. Koliko često *izlaze* novi modeli mobilnih telefona? (How often do new models of mobile phones *come out*?)
9. Molim vas, *izlazite* iz mog kreveta. (Please *get out* of my bed.)
10. Bez obzira na vremenske uslove, oni uvek *izlaze* u šetnju. (Regardless of weather conditions, they always *go out* for a walk.)